ike":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>X隨即通知男友並且報警。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>Y不虞有詐，但向被告表示不能逗留太久，因晚上要到教堂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係講得好岩，無論有男友無男友，信教與不信教，港女都係雞，一有人撩，即刻濕晒，無一倖免。"},{"pid":"6d223a271dac0c0ca51252a0c6983f0c5ec2ff9f","tid":747381,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:43:08.000Z","msg":"無業青年涉非法禁銅及強姦兩女網友一案，今午續審。控方下午宣讀控辯雙方均同意的案情，透露首名女事主X疑被強姦後翌日，警方曾到被告屯門龍門居寓所搜證，在被告房內搜出8件各式各樣的性玩具、1條銀幼棒、9個未開封的避孕套及1個已經開封的避孕套，惟被告數天後再於同一單位涉強姦另一名女事主Y。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">控方將性玩具呈堂，有假陽具、震蛋，及兩條長達24.5及26厘米﹑外型粗大的黑色棒狀性玩具，有女陪審團看到有關性玩具時不禁皺眉。</span>"},{"pid":"1e2b8c10bd29c4bb99b436f8d31c2775589462c0","tid":747381,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb84a72fa116c341d41167a6f126b519959a10f9","tid":747381,"uid":120093,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:44:54.000Z","msg":"X男友飛左佢未"},{"pid":"5f1707e05decb6520c6b3f44ac6bed84b4dd417f","tid":747381,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:46:32.000Z","msg":"有乜唔岩先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}